    "description": "<strong>Waves of Enemies attacking your Base. Mine Minerals to upgrade your Base. Buy Turrets. Increase your Base Range. Improve your Ships skills and stats. Try to survive as long as possible!</strong><br><br>Follow our Discord-Server if you want to stay up to date!<br><br><br><strong><u>Mining</u></strong><br>Mine Asteroids by flying close to them! The Minerals mined can be spend to upgrade your Base!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286750/extras/489cb7ee1b347ff7a064fcf54c31dba1.poster.avif?t=1675325063\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286750/extras/489cb7ee1b347ff7a064fcf54c31dba1.webm?t=1675325063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286750/extras/489cb7ee1b347ff7a064fcf54c31dba1.mp4?t=1675325063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Player Upgrades!</u></strong><br>Choose Cards to improve you Ship as you like. More Mining-Range? More Attack-Speed? You want a Turret following you? No Problem!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286750/extras/b1277a28ec0efac945e3c294abbdd0a2.poster.avif?t=1675325063\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286750/extras/b1277a28ec0efac945e3c294abbdd0a2.webm?t=1675325063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286750/extras/b1277a28ec0efac945e3c294abbdd0a2.mp4?t=1675325063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Base Upgrades!</u></strong><br>Buy Turrets, Increase Stats  &amp; Upgrade your Base. Spend the Minerals you mined from Asteroids for powerfull Upgrades to make you survive longer!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286750/extras/8ea0de16a0520c485b0f0b59b5dc8c85.poster.avif?t=1675325063\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286750/extras/8ea0de16a0520c485b0f0b59b5dc8c85.webm?t=1675325063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286750/extras/8ea0de16a0520c485b0f0b59b5dc8c85.mp4?t=1675325063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Weapons!</u></strong><br>After 5 Waves you can choose a Weapon that slightly enhances you to play different. You take the Miner-Weapon? Mine the hell outa' those Asteroids and go for Turrets. You take the Sniper? Execute High Level Enemies within seconds! You like Explosions? BOOM! Rocket-Launcher. Flame-Thrower? Burn. Them. Down!!<br><br><u>Rocket-Launcher</u><br>Exploding-Bullets deal massive AOE-Damage!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286750/extras/11d7920a7b3a4165431ba1c9fb77c511.poster.avif?t=1675325063\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286750/extras/11d7920a7b3a4165431ba1c9fb77c511.webm?t=1675325063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286750/extras/11d7920a7b3a4165431ba1c9fb77c511.mp4?t=1675325063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Sniper</u><br>Powerfull Single-Target Bullets execute Enemies!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286750/extras/2ce19fa3caa1504317d68380e